{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"56707-kinene-nyo-kitono-nyo","title":"Too Big! Too Small!","description":"Shamu munene nyo ku Ammi okusitula. Ate mutono nyo okugenda kusomero yeka. Oli muto nyo okusoma akataba weka? oba olimukulu okusoma nomuntu ? kabikule olabe...","language":"Luganda","langCode":"lg","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Bulyaba Ruth"],"illustrators":["Lavanya Karthik"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"AfLIA","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/56707-kinene-nyo-kitono-nyo"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42852/size3/0a1060a113ec19cf656ea8d7ef5b0ad9.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42852/size6/0a1060a113ec19cf656ea8d7ef5b0ad9.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42853/size6/70fd0452aa6c927e53d76aa9fb3f4ffc.jpg","text":"Sisobola kusitula wagulu Shanu! Ammi yagamba.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42854/size6/fc8e07ddde1f569112ef4235e88c71fd.jpg","text":"\"Tosobola kutambula kusomelo weka,\" Abudu yagamba.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42855/size6/a26479a6b4ec64005cc22f1749c54a41.jpg","text":"\"Tosobola kwebaka mukatenda ka mwena Shanu, \" Dudu yagamba.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42856/size6/0a0aa02709c207420750b383dd405ace.jpg","text":"\"Tosobola kusitula mwana kumutwala wakuzanyila Shanu.\" Dadi yagamba.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42857/size6/8e306b49594a4a1a1f6c925